title: LI190SB replaced
description: The LI190SB (serial # Q46275) was drifting and was replaced with another  LI190SB (serial # Q46277). However the multiplier was not updated for the  new sensor or corrected (the old multiplier was not calculated correctly) due  to computer problems (crashed while sending new program). The multiplier  was corrected on 2017-05-09 once I had a new field laptop.

external_refs.identifier: LI190SB replaced; see incident report IR_526
